1.ami tmr hasbent,eta kuno bisoy na tmr kase, & jamai hole kotha shunte hobe,mante hobe jamaike eta islame nai,taina?

2.nijer baper takai kacco ami bokar k? amr tmr jamai hoisi ki hoise amr odikar nai tmk bokar,taina?



1.rijon boro hoye tk earn korte onk late ase, 
2.amk allah samorto dile tmdr barir boro cheler dayitto ami palon korbo,
3.tmr abbu ammu ja lage sob ami dibo in sha allah,ami dile to nibena , tmr maddome dibo, onara taw nibena,so kisu gatty dekle kisu drkr ase bole mone holei chupcap amr kas theke tk niye /amr money bag theke niye jinish ta kine rakba,
4.ar rijon er boro vai o ami hobo,jodio ba ekn oke bokte boli karon ekto beshi disturb kore tai, tmr vai mane amro chuto vai,tmr family mane amri family. 
5.eta amr wada tmr kase,amr samorto hole in sha allah tmdr vasar bisesh kore tmr abbu ammur deka shuna ami korbo.& rijon k income kora obdi or
